NBA ALL-STAR WEEKEND
February 13, 2009
Arron Afflalo
START_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT
 
 
  
 
  
  
   
  Q. Do you have a strategy for tomorrow night?  
 ARRON AFFLALO: Just make the shot. You don't worry too much, just make sure you make the shot.  
  
  Q. As far as the rest of the season, you guys made a trade for Iverson. Talk a little bit about the remaining games you have left.   
 ARRON AFFLALO: We expect to come out strong. We expect to play well. We expect to play hard.   
 It is a matter of focusing night in and night out, maintain that intensity. Doing what we can do best. We have the personnel to be a great team.  
   
  End of FastScripts  
  

END_OF_INTERVIEW_TEXT